title: Dog Riding Wave - 2009 Dog Surfing Contest - Helen Woodward Animal Shelter
description:
Photos and Video Footage from the 2009 Helen Woodward Surf Dog Contest

Check out a quick clip from the 2009 Helen Woodward Dog Surfing Contest Event featuring surfing dogs from all over San Diego and Orange County. These dogs have a lot of courage and surf to raise money for homeless pets and animals.

asset.author: SoCal Beaches Magazine

www.socalbeachmag.net - Photos and Video Footage from the 2009 Helen Woodward Surf Dog Contest

Check out a quick clip from the 2009 Helen Woodward Dog Surfing Contest Event featuring surfing dogs from all over San Diego and Orange County. These dogs have a lot of courage and surf to raise money for homeless pets and animals.  

For more photos and video from the event visit www.socalbeachmag.net

For more information on the Helen Woodward Animal Shelter and their programs visit www.animalcenter.org
